16:33.120 --> 16:34.980
Nanti kami berdua akan sering pulang.

16:34.980 --> 16:36.640
Pasti sering-sering pulang.

16:39.140 --> 16:40.240
Sayang.

16:40.340 --> 16:41.740
Datang, datang, datang.

16:41.940 --> 16:42.500
